Welcome to 8809 W Frier Dr, a pristine oasis in Glendale's Rovey Farm subdivision. This 5-bed, 3-bath gem radiates pride of ownership and modern allure. The 3-car garage, with newly coated epoxy floors, adds a touch of luxury. Step inside to discover a flawlessly upgraded kitchen featuring granite counters and brand-new stainless steel appliances.
The entire home exudes cleanliness and style with new engineered hardwood floors, chic white/grey tones, and custom built-ins. Your oasis awaits in the newly replastered, fenced pool surrounded by artificial grass and lush landscaping.Enjoy move-in readiness with two new A/C units, solar panels, and window screens ensuring low bills and summer comfort. Nestled against a greenbelt, privacy and scenic charm abound. With proximity to the Westgate. List of Upgrades in 8809 West Frier Drive in Glendale, Az 
"	TWO New A/Cs
"	New Solar 
"	Solar Window Screens (keeping summer temperatures down)
"	Sparkling FENCED Pool NEWLY REPLASTERED
"	New Engineered Hard Wood Floors
"	New Hot Water Heater
"	New Kitchen Stainless Steel Appliances (Dishwasher, Microwave, Refrigerator and more...)
"	Granite
"	All White Cabinets
"	Modern Custom Built-Ins throughout
Welcome to 8809 West Frier Drive in Glendalea masterpiece of modern living and luxurious upgrades! This stunning residence, located in the sought-after Rovey Farm subdivision, boasts a plethora of features that redefine comfort and style.

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the meticulous attention to detail and pride of ownership. The chic white/grey color palette sets the tone for the sophisticated ambiance that permeates throughout this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home. The 3-car garage, complete with a newly coated epoxy floor and built-in cabinets, provides ample space for both vehicles and storage.

The heart of this home is the newly upgraded kitchen, featuring granite counters and a suite of brand-new stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher, microwave, and refrigerator. The all-white cabinets add a touch of modern elegance, complemented by custom built-ins throughout the residence.

Escape the Arizona heat in your sparkling, newly replastered, fenced pool, surrounded by recently landscaped grounds that include vibrant artificial grass and a state-of-the-art sprinkler and drip system. The exterior also boasts new garage doors, ensuring a seamless blend of style and functionality.

Energy efficiency takes center stage with two brand-new air conditioning units, solar panels, and solar window screens that keep summer temperatures at bay, all contributing to lower electric bills. Inside, the ambiance is further enhanced by new engineered hardwood floors, adding warmth and sophistication.

Convenience meets lifestyle with proximity to the Westgate Entertainment District, schools in the Peoria Unified School District within walking distance, parks, the 101 freeway, and shoppingall within reach. Enjoy the added privacy and scenic charm of being nestled against a greenbelt.

This exquisitely renovated home is not just move-in ready; it's a testament to the perfect blend of functionality and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream homeschedule a showing today and experience the epitome of Arizona living!
